Optometron of Omniscience*
He who posesses the Optometron of Omniscience will know everything. You
will always know what is under any explored cell. You will always know
which spells are which during your bonus spell selections. You will always
know the stats of ANY scroll that you examnine. You will be able to freely
read the minds of the other wizards to know what spells are in their
spell-lists. + more! The Optometron of Omniscience is functionally
equivalent to possessing a Recognomancer and Burstroem's Browser + more.

During the spell-selection phase, just press CTRL-# to browse through
another player's spell-list. E. G. press ctrl-2 to peek at player 2's
spell-list.
